<div id="recommendedReads" class="recommended-reads d-none d-sm-none d-md-none d-lg-block d-xl-block">
<h2 class="recommended-reads__intro-text">
2023 Forward Prizes </h2>
<a href="https://granta.com/withstances/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Rowan-Evans-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Rowan-Evans-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
Withstances </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘I alone know a running stream
that is recovery partly and dim sweat
of a day-fever’
<br><br>
A poem by Rowan Evans. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/in-conversation-mehri-shire/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Mehri_Shire_image3-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Mehri_Shire_image3-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
In Conversation </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘Humour is a thread we hang onto. It punctures through the fog of guilt.’<br><br>
Momtaza Mehri in conversation with Warsan Shire. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/in-conversation-mary-jean-chan-andrew-mcmillan/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/In-Convo-Chan-McMillan-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/In-Convo-Chan-McMillan-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
In Conversation </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘Something shifted in me that night. A small voice in my head said, maybe you can make a way for yourself as a poet here, too.’<br><br>
Mary Jean Chan in conversation with Andrew McMillan. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/joy-and-insecurity-in-port-au-prince/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Allen-Paisant_cropped-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Allen-Paisant_cropped-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
