<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
Joy and Insecurity in Port-au-Prince </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘There was to be an exhibition. There were lots of pictures like his, apparently – of waiters, pastry cooks, valets, bellboys.’<br><br>An essay by Jason Allen-Paisant from <em>Granta</em> 159: What Do You See? </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
<a href="https://granta.com/naming-allen-paisant/">
<div class="recommended-reads__item">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
<div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
<img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Allen-Paisant-100x100.jpg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Allen-Paisant-100x100.jpg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript> </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
<h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
Naming </h3>
<p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
‘I have started to see that nothing is itself’<br><br>A poem by Jason Allen-Paisant from <em>Granta</em> 154: I’ve Been Away for a While. </p>
</div>
